statements: SELECT * FROM WasteManagement
SELECT project_name, quantity FROM WasteManagement WHERE waste_type = 'Plastic'
SELECT project_name, disposal_method FROM WasteManagement WHERE quantity > 100
SELECT * FROM WasteManagement WHERE project_id IN (1, 3, 5)
SELECT project_name, waste_type FROM WasteManagement ORDER BY project_name DESC
SELECT * FROM WasteManagement WHERE waste_type = 'Plastic' ORDER BY quantity DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT project_name, quantity FROM WasteManagement WHERE disposal_method = 'Recycling' ORDER BY project_name ASC
SELECT * FROM WasteManagement WHERE quantity > 100 AND disposal_method = 'Landfill'
SELECT project_id, project_name, waste_type, quantity FROM WasteManagement WHERE quantity BETWEEN 50 AND 200 ORDER BY project_id
SELECT * FROM WasteManagement WHERE project_name LIKE '%Project%'
SELECT * FROM BuildingProjects;
SELECT project_name, project_location FROM BuildingProjects;
SELECT project_name, project_start_date, project_end_date FROM BuildingProjects WHERE project_location = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM WasteManagement;
SELECT waste_type, waste_weight, waste_date FROM WasteManagement WHERE project_id = '12345678-90ab-cdef-1234-567890abcdef';
SELECT project_name, project_location FROM BuildingProjects;
SELECT * FROM BuildingProjects WHERE project_start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT project_name, project_location, project_start_date, project_end_date FROM BuildingProjects WHERE project_location LIKE '%City%';
SELECT project_name, project_location FROM BuildingProjects ORDER BY project_start_date DESC;
SELECT wp.waste_type, wp.waste_weight, bp.project_name FROM WasteManagement wp JOIN BuildingProjects bp ON wp.project_id = bp.project_id WHERE wp.waste_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM waste_management_project;
SELECT project_id, project_name, project_location FROM waste_management_project;
SELECT project_id, project_name, project_location, waste_type FROM waste_management_project WHERE waste_type = 'Recyclables';
SELECT * FROM disposal_sites WHERE site_capacity > 1000;
SELECT site_location, site_capacity FROM disposal_sites ORDER BY site_capacity DESC;
SELECT * FROM waste_management_project WHERE waste_type = 'Plastic';
SELECT project_name, waste_type FROM waste_management_project ORDER BY project_name DESC;
SELECT project_name, project_location FROM waste_management_project WHERE project_location LIKE '%City%' AND waste_type = 'Paper';
SELECT project_name, project_location FROM waste_management_project WHERE project_location != 'Industrial Area' OR waste_type IS NULL;

SELECT wmp.project_name, wc.collection_date, wc.collection_weight FROM waste_management_project wmp JOIN waste_collection wc ON wmp.project_id = wc.project_id WHERE wc.collection_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Contractors WHERE contractor_name = 'ABC Construction'

SELECT project_name, contractor_name FROM Projects p JOIN Contractors c ON p.contractor_id = c.id

SELECT * FROM GreenBuildings;
SELECT building_name, location FROM GreenBuildings WHERE building_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM WasteBins WHERE bin_capacity > 100;
SELECT building_name, bin_capacity FROM GreenBuildings INNER JOIN WasteBins ON GreenBuildings.building_id = WasteBins.bin_id;
SELECT log_date, quantity FROM WasteManagementLogs ORDER BY log_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT building_name, location FROM GreenBuildings ORDER BY building_name ASC;
